- Baiklah.

256
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:13,050
- Pelan-pelan.
- Tiupkan ini juga.

257
00:22:20,719 --> 00:22:21,959
Ibu memang hebat.

258
00:22:31,229 --> 00:22:32,269
Dae Young.

259
00:22:33,429 --> 00:22:35,900
