405
00:33:36,729 --> 00:33:37,830
Bukan begitu.

406
00:33:37,830 --> 00:33:40,330
Lalu apa?

407
00:33:40,870 --> 00:33:42,840
Ada apa?

408
00:33:43,639 --> 00:33:45,169
Kenapa kamu

409
